	(text "BQ25611D NVDC: hardware CE keeps charging disabled through reset. Firmware writes charge/OTG disabled first; 960 mA is the register step for the 1.0 A normal R0 policy; 1500 mA only after thermal validation. OTG remains disabled and charger D+/D- are test pads only.\nSamsung INR18650-35E reference cell: factory-welded tabs to plated PCB slots; cradle carries all mechanical load."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
