	(text "Y2 is Epson FC-135R X1A0001410001, 32.768 kHz, 7 pF on XTAL_32K_P/N. Validate load capacitance, startup and standby benefit; DNP Y2, C30 and C31 together if firmware does not use the external RTC clock."
