	(text "IM73A135 VDD is 2.75 V MICBIAS; place C51/C52 at the microphone. Configure ADC IN1 for the differential microphone path and keep OUT+/OUT- matched.\nEnclosure: use a sealed external acoustic chimney, isolated from the BMP581 ePTFE atmospheric vent. ADC channel 2 is routed to TP20/TP21 for test or optional expansion."
